{"tid":1683673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"～我發夢見到榮光終歸香港啦～","createTime":"2019-10-30T17:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T17:53:44.000Z","uid":228989,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e9cc6ee083c17d55a854afa57f1b30f9c5e25aa0","tid":1683673,"uid":228989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:32:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">The night is darkest just before the dawn. And I promise you, the dawn is coming. </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黎明前的夜晚是最黑暗的，但我承諾各位，黎明就要來到。</span></span>&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n出自Badman-The Dark Knight <br />\n<br />\n我發夢見到香港人除曬gear手足互攬係到喊<br />\n<br />\n我發夢見到香港人可以為已死去的死者得到平反<br />\n<br />\n我發夢見到香港人為已在天堂的義士說我地得左啦<br />\n<br />\n我發夢見到香港人被捕後可以脫罪冇留案底<br />\n<br />\n我發夢見到香港人見到法庭判決緊黑官黑警<br />\n<br />\n我發夢見到香港人可以普選政府<br />\n<br />\n我發夢見到香港人可以對將來既囝囡講事蹟唱榮光<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人只要繼續堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n榮光終歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求    缺一不可<br />\n光復香港    時代革命"},{"pid":"5ae4f79195c10f62ebc8acbd6a22a802fbd9b712","tid":1683673,"uid":228989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:32:38.000Z","msg":"發夢自推1"},{"pid":"4ad842ae8e18027958acbfc0143b25c43c1758aa","tid":1683673,"uid":228989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:32:51.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"0aa025bb7d04cf9504ce2cbe20a00380c807f7ed","tid":1683673,"uid":228989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:33:09.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"eb5463d4134447f6d7bf438b907116b67b069ddf","tid":1683673,"uid":228989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:33:55.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"087d42546ab